{"id":277624,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-被关久敬庄获释的6名上访维权者到中纪委/","date":"2013-02-03T11:30:37Z","modified":"2013-02-03T11:30:37Z","title":"维权网 | 被关久敬庄获释的6名上访维权者到中纪委请愿（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员疾风报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分</span><span>，李春丽、李素莲、王新、马治国、王丽萍、刘华琼六人集会在中纪委门前请愿，抗议有关当局的非法关押，并要求为他们申冤，依法尽快解决他们的诉求。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点</span><span>左右，被关进久敬庄黑监狱的七名各地上访维权者，在恢复自由后坐地铁前往王府井，不料出站时被王府井站治安办公室警察拦截，带到治安办公室问话。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>中午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分左右，这七名访民被转送到久敬庄黑监狱关押。下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>分左右，王丽萍、刘华琼、许海燕三人被亲友接走。当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>分左右，李春丽、李素莲、王新、马治国四人也陆续获得自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>李春丽手机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15842247125</span></div>\n<div><span>李素莲手机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13264296036</span></div>\n<div><span>王新手机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15904030903</span></div>\n<div><span>马治国手机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13624210441</span></div>\n<div><span>王丽萍手机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13235653014</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>刘华琼手机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13911468798</span></div>\n<div><span>许海燕手机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13474401828</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-aIvfpmpiHh4/UQ5